# Saria’s BaSH testing library

[![Latest release][shield-release]][repo-url-releases]
[![Tests status][shield-workflow-run-tests]][repo-url-workflow-run-tests]
[![Top language][shield-language]][repo-url]
[![Licence][shield-license]][project-url-license]

Testing library for shell scripts.

Saria’s BaSH testing library is a single-file shell script that provides testing routines. It can be sourced into a script to create simple and clean testing scripts.


